_sText:
Glass War Pro.

Original Author: Smokey.

Map reworked by Robtronic.

Info:

Map has been fully optimized.

Map has better texture's.

Map has had layout changes
for overall better gameplay.

Map has now got 64 spawn's.

Nav is zipped into the bsp.

Other info:
The map was made from scratch
apart from the glass frame 
which i used as a template
so i could get the correct
map size and i also removed
the pit water but they is a
small amount of water in the pit
but you will have to be careful
as they is prop's in the pit
which will kill you if you land on
them. The map is now dm friendly.

Note's:
I only remade this map for the clan
server, everyone love'd it so i 
thought i'd share it with fpsbanana.
